<item>
            <title>[LU-18968] Build error in libcfs when enabling LNET_DUMP_ON_PANIC</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-18968</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;If the LNET_DUMP_ON_PANIC macro is defined by enabling the --enable-panic_dumplog option at configure time, an error occurs during the libcfs build process.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This error is due to specifying an incorrect parameter when calling the cfs_print_to_console() function within the cfs_trace_debug_print() function.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
